The schematic (schematic.sch) was drawn using the gEDA project (http://www.gpleda.org/)

The following libraries are required:
	- LiquidCrystal (included in the Arduino base pakage)
	- DS1307RTC (http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/td_libs_DS1307RTC.html)
	- TimeAlarms (http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/td_libs_TimeAlarms.html)
	- Time (http://www.pjrc.com/teensy/td_libs_Time.html)
